high_descs: Walk towards the wall, then turn right to face the white table.
Pick up the metal spatula off of the white table.
Turn right and walk forward, then hang a right and walk up to the white table.
Put the spatula in the glass bowl on the white table.
Pick up the glass bowl with the spatula in it off of the table.
Turn left and walk over to the counter.
Put the glass bowl with the spatula in it on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a glass bowl with a spatula in it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn right and face the table
Pick up the turner on the table
Turn right then head to the table beside the fridge
Put the turner in the bowl
Pick up the bowl with turner
Turn let then head to the sink counter
Put the bowl with turner on the sink counter in front of the plate
anns.task_desc: Put the bowl with turner on the sink counter

high_descs: Face the white table on the right.
Pick up the spatula from the center of the table.
Carry the spatula and turn around to the long white table.
Place the spatula in the bowl in the back of the table.
Pick up the bowl from the back of the table.
Carry the bowl and turn to the left and move to the counter.
Place the bowl on the counter, to the right of the sink in the back.
anns.task_desc: Move a spatula and bowl to the counter.
